{"tid":911461,"cid":35,"subCid":0,"title":"我係咪中緊伏？","createTime":"2018-11-22T02:43:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-22T02:52:41.000Z","uid":208536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"488b2b5bcf7583473e19995c4f41dac7aa1edd5f","tid":911461,"uid":208536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T02:43:15.000Z","msg":"事緣屋企今個月寬頻到期<br />\n本身用緊pccw 早2個月開個續約價鬼咁貴<br />\n就拖住先 咁岩有間HGC打黎<br />\n咁聽完offer 平又平啲<br />\n加少少可以供埋部電視<br />\n咁個陣幫我跟開個員工姓蘇<br />\n打去問幾次野<br />\n次次都唔知答案<br />\n每次都要收左線問完再打番黎<br />\nOkay啦去到今日裝機<br />\n約左11-1上黎<br />\n我見佢無人聯絡我<br />\n咁咪打番去個姓蘇既員工到<br />\n打左次無人聽 見就夠鐘<br />\n咁我咪上網搵HGC個電話打去<br />\n點撚知 個電話錄音把聲<br />\n同埋後來聽我電話個個客戶服務主任把聲<br />\n同姓蘇個個員工把聲好撚似<br />\n個客戶服務主任仲話自己姓蘇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我係咪中撚緊伏？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc2bb9b3f76f3065edccf6036b6e5850c89a735b","tid":911461,"uid":133528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T02:44:56.000Z","msg":"係<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb5d347ef6c5be47cb5e903223c0667d0d3aea23","tid":911461,"uid":208536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fc2bb9b3f76f3065edccf6036b6e5850c89a735b","tid":911461,"uid":133528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T02:44:56.000Z","msg":"係<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T02:48:23.000Z","msg":"成間公司得一個人？"},{"pid":"6f528e88b8b0c3b27653a5e28098f9bec0a7025f","tid":911461,"uid":208536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T02:50:41.000Z","msg":"仲有件事好奇怪<br />\n我打去個陣<br />\n佢要我入身份證號碼<br />\n咁入完禁完#<br />\n個個姓蘇既客戶服務主任<br />\n問我係咪 X先生<br />\n我話係<br />\n佢話 咁我叫師傅聯絡你啦<br />\n你手機係咪 6xxx xxxx<br />\n地址係咪 xxxxxxxxxx<br />\n佢無核實過我其他資料就講哂我啲資料出黎<br />\n係咪正常<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"361e4151c0c540b8f054aa0f9e463147e2528a4d","tid":911461,"uid":208536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T02:52:41.000Z","msg":"真心求助 推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}